<title>Lal Nunnem Vang Khuo !</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Hun leh ni lenkawl a liem
 Lungtuok gibang khennan
 Albang dahna meipi'n ei bawm,
 Gibang khenlohna gam ka ngai
 Lal nunnem vang khawpi thak nuom

[V2]
 Aw, lungtuokte, kikhen tai tiu
 Damtakin zal mangpha
 Pathien galvan bukim lau inla
 Nuoi zinmang dogal zo zel dingin

[V3]
 2. Albang dah luonthi nula
 Lungdeih gi bang khente
 Khaubang chieh lai veng zelin la
 Thepna dogal hung lien mahleh
 Lalpa Nangin mapui zelin

[V4]
 3. Zion thimthu sut dingin
 I lennau dang mahleh
 Hinna lenkawl enna munah
 Mi thiengtho leh Angel te tawh
 Kumsawt laituol ah leng taitiu.</lyrics>
</song>